Career

She has one older sister and one younger sister. She moved around often and spent most of her childhood in Coronado, California. She was raped as a teenager.

Hart attended college and was majoring in architecture and engineering, but she did not graduate.

Hart entered the adult film industry in April 2011 and she did her first scene in Cum Fiesta for Reality Kings. She was the Penthouse Pet of the Month for March 2013.

In January 2016, Hart announced via her Twitter account that she was pregnant.
